OL,3,CFamily of man who died from high
OL,4,Ccholesterol condition ask others to
OL,5,Cget tested
OL,7,FMike Clarke, 29, died a week after
OL,8,Fcollapsing from a heart attack in 2015
OL,9,Fduring a football match - despite
OL,10,Fmedical intervention where stents were
OL,11,Ffitted in his heart. Blood tests
OL,12,Frevealed Mike had high cholesterol,
OL,13,Fsomething his family had always
OL,14,Fstruggled with but never fully
OL,15,Funderstood.
OL,17,FMike's brother Simon said: "After my
OL,18,Fbrother's death, we all went for
OL,19,Ftests, I was found to have high
OL,20,Fcholesterol too and received support
OL,21,Fat Leighton Hospital's lipid clinic.
OL,26,@yD@\OU
