OL,7,F"Medication helped, but there were
OL,8,Fstill unanswered questions like why
OL,9,Fwas this affecting so many of us?"
OL,11,FSimon's Consultant referred him to a
OL,12,Fnew pilot service screening for
OL,13,FFamilial Hypercholesterolaemia (FH), a
OL,14,Fhereditary condition that causes
OL,15,Fextremely high cholesterol from birth
OL,16,Fand significantly increases the risk
OL,17,Fof early heart disease if left
OL,18,Funtreated.
OL,26,@qD@bO]
