OL,5,Cget tested
OL,7,FSimon, from Winsford, underwent
OL,8,Fgenetic testing through the service
OL,9,Fand a few months later received
OL,10,Fconfirmation that he had FH.
OL,12,F"It was hard to hear. No one wants a
OL,13,Flifelong condition but it wasn't
OL,14,Freally about me. It was about getting
OL,15,Fanswers for my family," said Simon.
OL,17,F"The genetic testing means I now know
OL,18,FI have a condition that, even with
OL,19,Fdiet and exercise, will always be
OL,20,Fpresent.
