OL,7,F"It allows us to plan and make sure
OL,8,Fthat when the children in our family
OL,9,Freach the age where they can be
OL,10,Ftested, we take that step and don't
OL,11,Fignore it."
OL,13,FThanks to Simon's diagnosis, cascade
OL,14,Ftesting began across the family. His
OL,15,Fnephew was just four when he lost his
OL,16,Ffather. Now 13, he has also tested
OL,17,Fpositive for FH and has already
OL,18,Fstarted medication.
