OL,7,F"He's been on treatment since he was
OL,8,F11 ` that's two years of risk
OL,9,Freduction already. We can't change
OL,10,Fwhat happened to my brother, but we
OL,11,Fcan try to stop it happening again."
OL,13,FSimon's story is just one of many that
OL,14,Fhighlight the impact of the FH genetic
OL,15,Ftesting pilot launched in 2022 across
OL,16,FCheshire and Merseyside. Now, the
OL,17,Fservice has been commissioned on a
OL,18,Frecurrent basis by NHS Cheshire and
OL,19,FMerseyside, with support from Health
OL,20,FInnovation North West Coast.
