OL,7,FThe service is delivered by Liverpool
OL,8,FHeart and Chest Hospital NHS
OL,9,FFoundation Trust and offers genetic
OL,10,Ftesting to individuals with suspected
OL,11,FFH, followed by family cascade testing
OL,12,Ffor first-degree relatives - parents,
OL,13,Fsiblings and children. Those diagnosed
OL,14,Freceive a personalised care plan,
OL,15,Fincluding lipid-lowering therapy.
OL,17,FSince the service was launched:
OL,19,FFH affects around one in 250 people,
OL,20,Fbut fewer than five per cent of cases
OL,21,Fare diagnosed.
