OL,7,FAs part of the Lifespan Pathway for
OL,8,FLipid Management 2024, services in
OL,9,FCheshire and Merseyside now aim to
OL,10,Foffer a cholesterol test to all adults
OL,11,Funder 40 at least once to help close
OL,12,Fthat gap.
OL,14,FTo find out more about diagnosis and
OL,15,Ftreatment of FH please visit the
OL,16,FHeartUK or BHF website.
